8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Khroma and Visme share a solid foundation of core features including Ai Generation, Export Formats. On the other hand, Visme uniquely offers Templates and Drag And Drop and Brand Kit and Collaboration and Animations and Stock Assets, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Khroma holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Visme scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Khroma and Visme offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Khroma's free tier and Visme's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
